<hr size="1"> 


<a NAME="top">
<h1>IV. Performing a QM/MM simulation of the system with Gromacs</h1>
<p>
<a NAME="intro">
<strong>QM/MM MD simulation</strong>
<p>
We now perform a short 1ps QM/MM equilibration simulation of the
system.
<p>
<font color=red>localhost:~>grompp -f qmmm1.mdp -p qmmm.top -n
qmmm.ndx -c qmmm1.gro
<p>
<font color=red>localhost:~>mdrun -v -o
<a href=./files/qmmm1out.gro><qmmm1out.gro</a>
</font>
<p>
In the next step we will use the structure after 1 ps to investigate
the effect of absorbing an excess electron on the stability of the
Thymine dimer.
